"{    \"translations\": [        {            \"english_version\": \"Many people were treated at Gaza's al-Shifa hospital after violence erupted. UN observers said many had gunshot wounds. Gaza's health ministry reported over 112 deaths. Gazan authorities blame Israeli soldiers for the deaths. President Joe Biden promised to air-drop food into Gaza to help the half a million people at risk of famine.\",            \"english_title\": \"Conflict in Gaza\",            \"translated_version\": \"Muchas personas fueron atendidas en el hospital al-Shifa de Gaza despu\u00e9s de que estallara la violencia. Observadores de la ONU dijeron que muchos ten\u00edan heridas de bala. El ministerio de salud de Gaza inform\u00f3 m\u00e1s de 112 muertes. Las autoridades de Gaza culpan a los soldados israel\u00edes de las muertes. El presidente Joe Biden prometi\u00f3 lanzar comida en paraca\u00eddas a Gaza para ayudar a medio mill\u00f3n de personas en riesgo de hambruna.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Conflict in Gaza\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"A large crowd gathered for the funeral of Alexei Navalny, a prominent Russian opposition leader. Thousands queued to pay respects at the cemetery. Dmitry Peskov, Vladimir Putin's spokesman, warned that protesters would face legal consequences, but few were arrested.\",            \"english_title\": \"Funeral of Alexei Navalny\",            \"translated_version\": \"Una gran multitud se reuni\u00f3 para el funeral de Alexei Navalny, un destacado l\u00edder de la oposici\u00f3n rusa. Miles hicieron fila para rendir homenaje en el cementerio. Dmitry Peskov, portavoz de Vladimir Putin, advirti\u00f3 que los manifestantes enfrentar\u00edan consecuencias legales, pero pocos fueron arrestados.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Funeral of Alexei Navalny\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Fitch downgraded New York Community Bancorp to a junk rating. The bank found 'material weaknesses' in its loan risk review process and replaced its CEO. NYCB shares fell by 26% in a day and have dropped by 65% this year.\",            \"english_title\": \"Downgrade of New York Community Bancorp\",            \"translated_version\": \"Fitch rebaj\u00f3 la calificaci\u00f3n de New York Community Bancorp a basura. El banco encontr\u00f3 'debilidades materiales' en su proceso de revisi\u00f3n de riesgos de pr\u00e9stamos y reemplaz\u00f3 a su CEO. Las acciones de NYCB cayeron un 26% en un d\u00eda y han bajado un 65% este a\u00f1o.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Downgrade of New York Community Bancorp\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Walgreens and CVS will start selling mifepristone, an abortion drug, in some states. This marks the first time the medication will be available at retail pharmacies in America. The Supreme Court will hear a case that could impact access to the drug.\",            \"english_title\": \"Walgreens and CVS Selling Abortion Drug\",            \"translated_version\": \"Walgreens y CVS comenzar\u00e1n a vender mifepristona, una pastilla para abortar, en algunos estados. Esto marca la primera vez que el medicamento estar\u00e1 disponible en farmacias minoristas en Am\u00e9rica. La Corte Suprema escuchar\u00e1 un caso que podr\u00eda afectar el acceso a la pastilla.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Walgreens and CVS Selling Abortion Drug\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Kenya and Haiti agreed to send 1,000 Kenyan policemen to help tackle gang violence. The plan was initially blocked by Kenya's top court but has now been implemented. Haiti saw nearly 5,000 deaths due to gang-related violence last year.\",            \"english_title\": \"Kenyan Police Sent to Haiti\",            \"translated_version\": \"Kenia y Hait\u00ed acordaron enviar 1,000 polic\u00edas kenianos para ayudar a combatir la violencia de pandillas. El plan fue bloqueado inicialmente por el tribunal superior de Kenia, pero ahora se ha implementado. Hait\u00ed tuvo casi 5,000 muertes debido a la violencia relacionada con pandillas el a\u00f1o pasado.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Kenyan Police Sent to Haiti\"        }    ]}"